F=ax^2+2bxy+cy^2
x^2+y^2=1
A=\begin{bmatrix}a&b\\b&c\end{bmatrix}
z=\begin{bmatrix}x\\y\end{bmatrix}
F=ax^2+2bxy+cy^2=z^TAz
x^2+y^2=1=z^Tz
\max~~~z^TAz ~~\text{subject to}~z^Tz=1 \tag{1}
\min~~~z^TAz ~~\text{subject to}~z^Tz=1\tag{2}
\max
A
z=\begin{bmatrix}x\\y\end{bmatrix}
\min
A
z=\begin{bmatrix}x\\y\end{bmatrix}
A=\begin{bmatrix}a&b\\b&c\end{bmatrix}
